name: Amazon Overview
description: The Overview folder provides Account and Region level overview dashboards.

children.name: 1. AWS Account Overview
children.description: This dashboard provide detail information about your AWS account.
children.title: 1. AWS Account Overview

queries.queryString: namespace=AWS/Lambda metric=Errors statistic=Sum account={{account}} region=* functionname=* | sum
namespace=aws/dynamodb (metric=*Errors or metric=ConditionalCheckFailedRequests) Statistic=SampleCount account={{account}} region=* | sum
namespace=AWS/EC2 metric=CPU_Total account={{account}} region=* instanceId=* | avg
namespace=aws/rds metric=CPUUtilization statistic=average account={{account}} region=* dbidentifier=* | avg
namespace=AWS/EC2 account={{account}} metric=Mem_Free region=* instanceId=* | eval _value / 1073741824 | avg
namespace=aws/rds metric=FreeableMemory statistic=average account={{account}} region=* dbidentifier=* | eval _value / 1073741824 | avg
Namespace=AWS/ApiGateway (metric=4XXError or metric=5XXError) statistic=Sum account={{account}} region=* apiname=* | sum by apiname, namespace, region, account

Namespace=AWS/ApplicationELB (metric=HTTPCode_ELB_4XX_Count or metric=HTTPCode_ELB_5XX_Count) statistic=Sum account={{account}} region=* loadbalancer=* | sum by loadbalancer, namespace, region, account
Namespace=AWS/ApiGateway metric=count Statistic=sum account={{account}} region=* apiname=* | sum by apiname, namespace, region, account
Namespace=aws/applicationelb metric=RequestCount Statistic=Sum account={{account}} region=* loadbalancer=* | sum by loadbalancer, namespace, region, account
Namespace=aws/lambda metric=Invocations statistic=Sum account={{account}} region=* functionname=* | sum by functionname, namespace, region, account
Namespace=aws/dynamodb metric=SuccessfulRequestLatency Statistic=SampleCount account={{account}} region=* tablename=* | sum by tablename, namespace, region, account | eval round(_value)
namespace=aws/ecs metric=CPUUtilization statistic=Average account={{account}} region=* ClusterName=* | avg
namespace=aws/ecs metric=MemoryUtilization statistic=Average account={{account}} region=* ClusterName=* | avg
namespace=aws/elasticache metric=CPUUtilization statistic=Average account={{account}} region=* CacheClusterId=* | avg
Namespace=AWS/NetworkELB metric=*TLSNegotiationErrorCount statistic=Sum account={{account}} region=* loadbalancer=* | sum by loadbalancer, namespace, region, account
Namespace=aws/networkelb metric=ActiveFlowCount Statistic=Sum account={{account}} region=* loadbalancer=* | sum by loadbalancer, namespace, region, account
Namespace=aws/NetworkELB metric=HealthyHostCount Statistic=sum account={{account}} region=* LoadBalancer=* AvailabilityZone=* TargetGroup=* | sum
Namespace=aws/NetworkELB metric=UnHealthyHostCount Statistic=sum account={{account}} region=* LoadBalancer=* AvailabilityZone=* TargetGroup=* | sum
namespace=aws/elasticache metric=FreeableMemory statistic=average account={{account}} region=* CacheClusterId=* CacheNodeId=* | eval _value / 1073741824 | avg

"\"eventsource\"" account={{account}} sourceIPAddress
| json "eventTime", "eventName", "eventSource", "awsRegion", "userAgent", "recipientAccountId", "userIdentity", "requestParameters", "responseElements", "errorCode", "errorMessage",  "requestID", "sourceIPAddress" as eventTime, event_name, event_source, Region, user_agent, accountId1, userIdentity, requestParameters, responseElements, errorCode, errorMessage, requestID, src_ip nodrop
| where event_source matches "*amazonaws.com" and !(src_ip matches "*.amazonaws.com")
| count by src_ip
| lookup latitude, longitude from geo://location on ip = src_ip
| where !isnull(latitude)
account={{account}} Namespace=AWS/ELB metric=Latency Statistic=Average region=* loadbalancername=* | eval(_value*1000) | avg by account, region, namespace, loadbalancername
account={{account}} Namespace=AWS/ELB (metric=HTTPCode_ELB_4XX or metric=HTTPCode_ELB_5XX) Statistic=Sum region=* loadbalancername=* | sum by account, region, namespace, loadbalancername
Namespace=AWS/ELB metric=RequestCount Statistic=Sum account={{account}} region=* loadbalancername=* | sum by loadbalancername, namespace, region, account
account={{account}} Namespace=AWS/ApplicationELB metric=ActiveConnectionCount Statistic=Sum region=* loadbalancer=* | sum by account, region, namespace, loadbalancer
account={{account}} region=* namespace=aws/sns metric=NumberOfNotificationsDelivered Statistic=Sum topicname=* | sum
account={{account}} region=* namespace=aws/sns metric=NumberOfNotificationsFailed Statistic=Sum topicname=* | sum
account={{account}} region=* namespace=aws/sqs metric=NumberOfMessagesReceived Statistic=sum queuename=* | sum
account={{account}} region=* namespace=aws/sqs metric=NumberOfEmptyReceives Statistic=Sum queuename=* | sum

children.name: 1. AWS Region Overview
children.description: This dashboard provide detail information about your AWS account.
children.title: 1. AWS Region Overview

queries.queryString: namespace=AWS/Lambda metric=Errors statistic=Sum account={{account}} region={{region}} functionname=* | sum
namespace=aws/dynamodb (metric=*Errors or metric=ConditionalCheckFailedRequests) Statistic=SampleCount account={{account}} region={{region}} | sum
namespace=AWS/EC2 metric=CPU_Total account={{account}} region={{region}} instanceId=* | avg
namespace=aws/rds metric=CPUUtilization statistic=average account={{account}} region={{region}} dbidentifier=* | avg
namespace=AWS/EC2 account={{account}} metric=Mem_Free region={{region}} instanceId=* | eval _value / 1073741824 | avg
namespace=aws/rds metric=FreeableMemory statistic=average account={{account}} region={{region}} dbidentifier=* | eval _value / 1073741824 | avg
Namespace=AWS/ApiGateway (metric=4XXError or metric=5XXError) statistic=Sum account={{account}} region={{region}} apiname=* | sum by apiname, namespace, region, account

Namespace=AWS/ApplicationELB (metric=HTTPCode_ELB_4XX_Count or metric=HTTPCode_ELB_5XX_Count) statistic=Sum account={{account}} region={{region}} loadbalancer=* | sum by loadbalancer, namespace, region, account

"\"eventsource\"" account={{account}} sourceIPAddress
| json "eventTime", "eventName", "eventSource", "awsRegion", "userAgent", "recipientAccountId", "userIdentity", "requestParameters", "responseElements", "errorCode", "errorMessage",  "requestID", "sourceIPAddress" as eventTime, event_name, event_source, Region, user_agent, accountId1, userIdentity, requestParameters, responseElements, errorCode, errorMessage, requestID, src_ip nodrop
| where event_source matches "*amazonaws.com" and !(src_ip matches "*.amazonaws.com") and region matches "{{region}}"
| count by src_ip
| lookup latitude, longitude from geo://location on ip = src_ip
| where !isnull(latitude)
Namespace=AWS/ApiGateway metric=count Statistic=sum account={{account}} region={{region}} apiname=* | sum by apiname, namespace, region, account
Namespace=aws/applicationelb metric=RequestCount Statistic=Sum account={{account}} region={{region}} loadbalancer=* | sum by loadbalancer, namespace, region, account
Namespace=aws/lambda metric=Invocations statistic=Sum account={{account}} region={{region}} functionname=* | sum by functionname, namespace, region, account
Namespace=aws/dynamodb metric=SuccessfulRequestLatency Statistic=SampleCount account={{account}} region={{region}} tablename=* | sum by tablename, namespace, region, account | eval round(_value)
namespace=aws/elasticache metric=CPUUtilization statistic=Average account={{account}} region={{region}} CacheClusterId=* | avg
namespace=aws/ecs metric=CPUUtilization statistic=Average account={{account}} region={{region}} ClusterName=* | avg
namespace=aws/ecs metric=MemoryUtilization statistic=Average account={{account}} region={{region}} ClusterName=* | avg
Namespace=aws/networkelb metric=ActiveFlowCount Statistic=Sum account={{account}} region={{region}} loadbalancer=* | sum by loadbalancer, namespace, region, account
Namespace=aws/NetworkELB metric=HealthyHostCount Statistic=sum account={{account}} region={{region}} LoadBalancer=* AvailabilityZone=* TargetGroup=* | sum
Namespace=aws/NetworkELB metric=UnHealthyHostCount Statistic=sum account={{account}} region={{region}} LoadBalancer=* AvailabilityZone=* TargetGroup=* | sum
Namespace=AWS/NetworkELB metric=*TLSNegotiationErrorCount statistic=Sum account={{account}} region={{region}} loadbalancer=* | sum by loadbalancer, namespace, region, account
namespace=aws/elasticache metric=FreeableMemory statistic=average account={{account}} region={{region}} CacheClusterId=* CacheNodeId=* | eval _value / 1073741824 | avg
Namespace=AWS/ELB metric=RequestCount Statistic=Sum account={{account}} region={{region}} loadbalancername=* | sum by loadbalancername, namespace, region, account
account={{account}} Namespace=AWS/ELB (metric=HTTPCode_ELB_4XX or metric=HTTPCode_ELB_5XX) Statistic=Sum region={{region}} loadbalancername=* | sum by account, region, namespace, loadbalancername
account={{account}} Namespace=AWS/ApplicationELB metric=ActiveConnectionCount Statistic=Sum region={{region}} loadbalancer=* | sum by account, region, namespace, loadbalancer
account={{account}} Namespace=AWS/ELB metric=Latency Statistic=Average region={{region}} loadbalancername=* | eval(_value*1000) | avg by account, region, namespace, loadbalancername
account={{account}} region={{region}} namespace=aws/sns metric=NumberOfNotificationsDelivered Statistic=Sum topicname=* | sum
account={{account}} region={{region}} namespace=aws/sns metric=NumberOfNotificationsFailed Statistic=Sum topicname=* | sum
account={{account}} region={{region}} namespace=aws/sqs metric=NumberOfMessagesReceived Statistic=sum queuename=* | sum
account={{account}} region={{region}} namespace=aws/sqs metric=NumberOfEmptyReceives Statistic=Sum queuename=* | sum
